---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import EmailCapture from '../components/EmailCapture.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Start here" description="New to paw and sage? Begin here.">
  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <span class="eyebrow">Welcome</span>
      <h1>Start here.</h1>
      <p class="lede">If you're new to paw and sage, these are the best places to begin — depending on what brought you here.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="paths-section">
    <div class="container-narrow">

      <div class="path">
        <h2>I just got a new cat or kitten</h2>
        <p>Start with our <a href="/categories/new-cat">New Cat thread</a>. The most useful first read is <a href="/blog">our complete kitten checklist</a> (coming soon) — everything you actually need in the first week, in the order you'll need it.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="path">
        <h2>My cat is doing something weird</h2>
        <p>Head to <a href="/categories/behavior">Behavior</a>. Cats communicate constantly — most "weird" behavior has a clear explanation once you know what to look for.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="path">
        <h2>My indoor cat seems bored</h2>
        <p>You're probably right. <a href="/categories/enrichment">Enrichment</a> is our largest section, with practical ideas that take five minutes to set up — most under $30.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="path">
        <h2>I'm worried about my cat's health</h2>
        <p>Our <a href="/categories/health">Health thread</a> covers the signals worth noticing. Important: nothing here replaces a vet. We'll always tell you when to call one.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="email-section">
        <EmailCapture />
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-header { padding: 5rem 0 2rem; text-align: center; }
  .page-header .eyebrow { display: block; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .lede {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    max-width: 560px;
    margin: 1rem auto 0;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .paths-section { padding: 2rem 0 5rem; }
  .path {
    padding: 2rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .path:last-of-type { border-bottom: none; }
  .path h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
  }
  .path p {
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .email-section { margin-top: 3rem; }
</style>
